        detailed: 'Build contact form with full validation. Fields: name (required, min 2 chars), email (required, valid email format), subject (optional dropdown or text), message (required, min 10 chars, textarea with character counter). Layout: single column, proper spacing (space-y-4), labels above inputs. Styling: consistent input styles (border rounded-lg p-3), focus ring. Validation: inline error messages (text-red-600 text-sm). Submit button: primary style, loading state with spinner. Success state: replace form with thank you message.',
